Installing dependencies
-----------------------

For example, on *buntu systems, use the following commands:
	* sudo su
	* apt-get install build-essential libboost-all-dev libqt4-dev fftw3-dev wget
	* wget http://www.cern.ch/mathlibs/sw/5_34_14/Minuit2/Minuit2-5.34.14.tar.gz
	* tar -xzvf Minuit2-5.34.14.tar.gz
	* cd Minuit2-5.34.14
	* ./configure
	* make && make install
	* exit



Building Cattus
---------------

	* 'cd' into the miezetools directory
	* Get tlibs: ./setup_tlibs.sh
	* Compile using: ./build.sh
	* Run with: ./cattus
